## 8. Silver: limpeza + deduplicação + contrato lógico

Se a Silver for tabela Parquet externa simples:

```sql
CREATE TABLE silver.pagamentos
WITH (
    format='PARQUET',
    external_location='s3://meu-lakehouse/silver/cobranca/pagamentos/'
)
AS
SELECT
    contrato_id,
    CAST(valor AS double) AS valor,
    CAST(data_pagamento AS date) AS data_pagamento,
    anomesdia,
    dt_ingestao
FROM bronze.pagamentos_raw
WHERE try_cast(valor AS double) IS NOT NULL;
```

Se a Silver precisar de idempotência / upsert, use Iceberg:

```sql
CREATE TABLE silver.pagamentos (
    contrato_id string,
    valor double,
    data_pagamento date,
    anomesdia int,
    dt_ingestao timestamp
)
PARTITIONED BY (anomesdia)
LOCATION 's3://meu-lakehouse/silver/cobranca/pagamentos/'
TBLPROPERTIES (
    'table_type'='ICEBERG',
    'format'='parquet'
);
```

